{"tid":1392533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中/ 資源整理】 得罪人民仲想走? 一定要識撚狗三寶","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:50:55.000Z","uid":249794,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"247d8a6ec24aa8abfe2c9f7a23162c55201cc22f","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:56:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">話說之前個禍必及家人post比連仔del左</span></span><br />\n利申 打機攻略討論，與現實所有事無關，如有雷同，實屬巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排大家都打緊好heat嘅online game，最難打一定係狗頭怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/8841311828/640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F8841311828%2F640&h=977209c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高攻高防有組織，正面打好難會贏<br />\n所以玩家要做嘅除左升lv升裝之外，仲要學識撚狗，慢慢扣佢地生命值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合各post資訊<br />\n想撚狗 一定要知撚狗三寶<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先咩係hit and run呢，打過機都知<br />\n狗頭怪雖然勁但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">總體移速慢，要一輪CD先發動到攻勢</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢話唔多講，直接睇以下post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377370/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377370/page/1</a> (戰略向)<br />\n模擬實戰效果: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1388451/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1388451/page/1</a> (中小型)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1338617/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1338617/page/1</a><br />\nHit and Run可以係野貓式，可以係有目標性，可以圍魏救趙，任君選擇<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">總之重點係突擊/ 轉場，唔係散水</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攻心，乃上策也<br />\n成本低，唔犯法，同時令到狗頭怪連休息時間都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>謹記物理傷害只會加強佢地意志，精神折磨先可以令佢地求生不得</strong></span><br />\n狗頭怪都有小狗頭同大狗頭，見到佢地一家大細一定要好好打招乎<br />\n記得仲要比佢地鄰居知道啊<br />\n資源: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382922/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382922/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(一定要裝)</strong></span><br />\n模擬每週活動: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381797/page/1</a> <strong>(有外國玩家搞更好，可以留個名)</strong><br />\n<br />\n最後所有玩家記得出門要帶<strong>麻包袋</strong>裝自己物品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲可以用黎cosplay!<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xoer.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/EY91QO112024_878210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xoer.cc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FEY91QO112024_878210.jpg&h=b578ec35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參考: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378251/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378251/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377117/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377117/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎各位玩家補充</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後大家一齊同我講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539c2f6618649b2d65cb77eafc319c014c68feed","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:56:22.000Z","msg":"Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋"},{"pid":"683952e00b4260d5a3da03ca874f4b323e844de0","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:56:35.000Z","msg":"Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0db9f7fac03af710b0f959ec1f514895d30bb3f","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2b68ca493bad1ba377ac03c8dfea1c0472bb2a","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:57:10.000Z","msg":"深夜10連冇難度"},{"pid":"f03941e0091051813491211e88d0e2b6cadaade7","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e427891d53855f57c6058af3af269bdb44335d8","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:59:17.000Z","msg":"Hit and Run，攻心，麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ce074beed09c7ae4f45f7bebf1c551a6ba94e9","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:05:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"750e6adefab7f4de505d7c815c9d907f5d9f3c04","tid":1392533,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:07:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ce870999d03984f76006a5754e9379ac214c720","tid":1392533,"uid":80107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:22:44.000Z","msg":"正 打怪系統愈嚟愈良善<br />\n有得揀就腳副本 又有每週特別怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1d50c2a3fe3c82cf6ec7776bd4655358301c89","tid":1392533,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce870999d03984f760